至少有八千位馬來西亞人成群結隊到街上反對一項提案，該提案打算讓學校使用英文教導數學與科學。警察使用[催淚彈](http://jelas.info/2009/03/08/bm-
for-sciencemaths-denouncing-the-violence-dissecting-the-issue/
"http://jelas.info/2009/03/08/bm-for-sciencemaths-denouncing-the-violence-
dissecting-the-issue/")驅散了人群。

